  { name = "Tropical_Kleene",        loc = 610,  build = "GREEN", proof-failures = 0, doc-failures = 0,
    note = """CLOSED 2026-04-26 evening. Historical failures (now fixed): 237 (sum_mono — needed ordered_ab_semigroup_add instance in Tropical_v2); 403 (not_distinct_decomp obtain, [v] vs v#[] desugaring — replaced with cycle_shortcutting wrapper); 474 (trop_mat_id le — trop_add_le_iff needed); 575 (sum f S ≤ c — sum_le_const generalised to 'a ⇒ tropical). Doc-antiquotation at 14/40/163/348/373/442/598 — cosmetic, closed by quote-string fixes.""" },
  { name = "Tropical_Determinants",  loc = 338,  build = "GREEN", proof-failures = 0, doc-failures = 0,
    note = """CLOSED 2026-04-26 (1cb03e9 + e0d95e9). Root: Isabelle 2025-1 generalised permutes_in_image binding, leaving `0 :: ??'a` unconstrained. Fix: explicit `permutes_in_image[OF h, of 0/1]` pinning. Cascade-closed 81/153/166/191/207/262/302 (all 7 sites). Fun.swap → Transposition.transpose for 2x2 case (Fun.swap became input-only in 2025-1).""" },
  { name = "Tropical_Matrices_Full", loc = 2308, build = "GREEN", proof-failures = 0, doc-failures = 0,
    note = """CLOSED 2026-04-26 (512892d cycle-excise refactor + e0d95e9). Historical root 1525 (OF: multiple unifiers): strengthened path_weight_cycle_excise to explicit position pair. Cascade-closed 838/1874/2044. Doc-antiquotation at 48/1666 closed by quoting fixes.""" },
  { name = "Tropical_CNO",           loc = 1013, build = "GREEN", proof-failures = 0, doc-failures = 0,
    note = """CLOSED 2026-04-26 (34ae52e + cab5da8). Real proof gap: trop_mat_star_idem requires no_pos_cycle — now explicit assumption. trop_cno_star → trop_cno_star_conditional. walk_concat_nonempty switched to induction; set(tl) ⊆ set step made explicit. Doc-antiquotation closed by comment rewrite.""" },
  { name = "Tropical_Matrices_Clean", loc = 1124, build = "NOT-BUILT", proof-failures = "?", doc-failures = "?",
